12 SUMMARY
1133 This amendment replaces the language in the resolve requiring the Department of
1144 Health and Human Services to use the funding provided by the resolve to support certified
1155 community behavioral health centers by increasing wages with language requiring the
1166 department to use the funding provided by the resolve to support certified community
1177 behavioral health centers by enhancement of the department's special certified community
1188 behavioral health clinic funding in a manner that enables the department to access the
1199 designated enhanced federal match for the program.
